an Cavaleiro]], January 2020.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.expressandstar.com/sport/football/wolverhampton-wanderers-fc/2020/01/07/wolves-sell-ivan-cavaleiro-to-fulham-for-around-15m/|title=Wolves sell Ivan Cavaleiro to Fulham for around \u00a315m|publisher=Express & Star |date=7 January 2020}}</ref>\n\n;Progression of record fee paid<ref name=\"Whos Who\"/>\n{|border=\"0\" class=\"wikitable\"\n!Date!!Player!!Bought from!!Fee\n|-\n|September 1963||{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Ray Crawford (footballer)|Ray Crawford]]||[[Ipswich Town F.C.|Ipswich Town]]||\u00a355,000\n|-\n|February 1968||{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Derek Parkin]]||[[Huddersfield Town F.C.|Huddersfield Town]]||\u00a380,000\n|-\n|July 1972||{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Steve Kindon]]||[[Burnley F.C.|Burnley]]||\u00a3100,000\n|-\n|September 1977||{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Paul Bradshaw (footballer born 1956)|Paul Bradshaw]]||[[Blackburn Rovers F.C.|Blackburn Rovers]]||\u00a3150,000\n|-\n|September 1979||{{flagicon|SCO}} '''[[Andy Gray (footballer born 1955)|Andy Gray]]'''||[[Aston Villa F.C.|Aston Villa]]||\u00a31,500,000\n|-\n|March 1995||{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Dean Richards (footballer)|Dean Richards]]||[[Bradford City A.F.C.|Bradford City]]||\u00a31,850,000\n|-\n|September 1999||{{flagicon|NGA}} [[Ade Akinbiyi]]||[[Bristol City F.C.|Bristol City]]||\u00a33,500,000\n|-\n|June 2009||{{flagicon|IRL}} [[Kevin Doyle]]||[[Reading F.C.|Reading]]||\u00a36,500,000\n|-\n|June 2010||{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Steven Fletcher (footballer)|Steven Fletcher]]||[[Burnley F.C.|Burnley]]||\u00a36,500,000\n|-\n|August 2016||{{flagicon|POR}} [[Ivan Cavaleiro]]||[[AS Monaco FC|Monaco]]||\u00a37,000,000\n|-\n|January 2017||{{flagicon|POR}} [[H\u00e9lder Costa (footballer)|H\u00e9lder Costa]]||[[S.L. Benfica|Benfica]]||\u00a313,000,000\n|-\n|July 2017||{{flagicon|POR}} [[R\u00faben Neves]]||[[FC Porto|Porto]]||\u00a315,800,000\n|-\n|August 2018||{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Adama Traor\u00e9 (footballer, born 1996)|Adama Traor\u00e9]]||[[Middlesbrough F.C.|Middlesbrough]]||\u0